title: Shyla vs. The McBrooms... Let's Talk About It
description:
Welcome back, FOOLS! We had so many things to talk to y'all about today, we couldn't focus on just one topic. Instead, we have THREE trending topics we're covering on the pod: Shyla Walker vs. Landon McBroom, Kylie Swimwear, and Soy La 69. And of course, we had to fill you in on how our weeks went... with a relationship update from Manny?!
